    "work_description": "- Provide labor and material to reroute wiring at corner of Living Room. All wiring to be routed into wall space. - Provide labor and material to remove and reconnect wiring between receptacles. - Provide labor and material to Install junction box at back corner of house to enable splicing and extension of all Mini Split system power and control wiring. - Provide labor and material to add (1) switched exterior outlet and (1) constant power exterior receptacle at back patio at left hand side of door. Switched receptacle to be mounted up high for plug in hanging lights. Install new 2-gang switch box at interior of house, adding switch for exterior switched receptacle. - Provide labor and material to install a dedicated 120-volt circuit at exterior Patio for possible future electric grill. - Provide labor and material to add a ceiling pendant light at Dining Room. Light fixture provided by customer, installed by Orient Electric. Light fixture to be centered in the box pattern of can lights. Convert switch box for Dining room lights into a 2-gang switch box, installing dimmers for the pendant light and for the recessed can lights. - Provide labor and material to install a new, 50-amp, 240-volt circuit for new Induction Range. Range receptacle to be flush mounted in the wall. - Provide labor and material to install 30-amp, 240-volt connection for Heat Pump Water Heater. Install junction box, leaving a (6¿), flexible conduit with wire for final electrical connection. - Provide labor and material to relocate single receptacle at back of garage. Install surface mount conduit and raise receptacle to Customer directed location. Receptacle is for Energy Recovery ventilator. - Provide labor and material to install a dedicated, 120-volt, 20-amp circuit, including wire and conduit from electrical panel to back wall of Garage. Install (2) quadraplex outlets at back wall work bench area and single pole light switch for work bench overhead light. Light fixture provided b",
